                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7262" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OB-0340</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8860 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">三维一体、激活组织：A公司研发中心的组织变革之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Three-Dimensional Integration and Organization Activation: the Organizational Reform of A Company&#39;s R&amp;D Center</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">朱茶芬，许欣芃</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">浙江大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">恒生电子股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">电子工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">研发部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">组织变革；研发组织；IPD；流程再造</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"> Organizational change, R&amp;D organization, IPD, process reengineering</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">A公司是中国金融软件行业的头部企业，在公司实行平台化转型的新战略驱动下，研发中心承担了公司技术平台的开发重任，这对研发中心的现有组织管理体系提出了严峻挑战。2021年，研发中心开启了全方位组织变革：在全面深入的组织诊断基础上，研发中心系统梳理了三大管理痛点：组织职责不清晰、流程制度不健全、预算考核不科学；随后，针对性地提出了“三维一体”的变革方案，聚焦全新战略定位，从组织职责、流程制度、预算考核三个维度进行组织再造，最终实现了组织效能的全面提升。当前，研发对于实现“中国创造”具有重大意义，如何提高研发组织效能已成为重要的管理议题，然而聚焦研发组织管理的案例研究极少。本案例聚焦于研发组织的管理变革，作为典型的知识型组织，研发组织的管理变革面临更多挑战。A公司研发中心“三维一体”的变革方案、科学高效的变革管理，能为其他企业的研发组织提供重要借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">As a leader in China&#39;s financial software industry, the R&amp;D center in Company A has taken up the development of technology platform under the new strategy of platform transformation, which poses a serious challenge to the existing organizational system. In 2021, the R&amp;D center started a comprehensive organizational change: based on an in-depth organizational diagnosis, the R&amp;D center systematically sorted out three major management problems: unclear organizational responsibilities, inadequate process system, and unscientific budget assessment. Then, it proposed a &quot;three-dimensional&quot; reform scheme, focusing on a new strategic positioning, and reengineering the organization from three dimensions: organization responsibilities, process system and budget assessment, which finally achieved an overall improvement of organization efficiency. At present, R&amp;D is important for realizing &quot;China Creation&quot;, and how to improve the effectiveness of R&amp;D organization has become an important issue, but there are few case studies about it. Company A&#39;s &quot;three-dimensional&quot; reform scheme and efficient reform management can provide important reference for other firms&#39; R&amp;D organizations.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《组织行为学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">知识型组织；战略-组织-流程框架；组织诊断方法；六个盒子理论；华为IPD；变革阻力和化解阻力的策略；变革领导</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-04</td>
                            </tr>
